PN,39601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FThose involved in the care and
OL,7,Fmonitoring of the Southport killer
OL,8,F'fundamentally failed' to appreciate
OL,9,Fthe "evident high level of danger" he
OL,10,Fposed - leading to an "act of chilling
OL,11,Fbrutality", an inquiry has found.
OL,13,FAxel Rudakubana, 19, was consistently
OL,14,Fpassed between organisations with a
OL,15,F"disturbing lack of clarity as to who,
OL,16,Fif anyone, was the lead" in ensuring
OL,17,Fthe risk he posed was communicated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FHis parents also had an "irresponsible
OL,7,Fand harmful attitude" to sharing
OL,8,Finformation, meaning they did not do
OL,9,Fwhat they "morally ought to have done"
OL,10,Fand "report the clear escalation in
OL,11,Frisk" which could - and should - have
OL,12,Fstopped the attack happening, it was
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FAs a consequence AR - as he has been
OL,16,Fknown throughout the inquiry - went on
OL,17,Fto murder Bebe King, six, Elsie Dot
OL,18,FStancombe, seven, and Alice da Silva
OL,19,FAguiar, nine, at a Taylor Swift-themed
OL,20,Fdance class on 29 July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FThe killer, then 17, also attempted to
OL,7,Fmurder eight other children, who
OL,8,Fcannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,9,Fclass instructor Leanne Lucas, and
OL,10,Fbusinessman John Hayes.
OL,12,FThe Southport Inquiry, held over nine
OL,13,Fweeks at Liverpool Town Hall in 2025,
OL,14,Flooked at what happened before and
OL,15,Fduring the attack, identifying missed
OL,16,Fopportunities and systemic failures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FIn a damning report Chair Sir Adrian
OL,7,FFulford concluded he was almost
OL,8,Fcertain "this terrible event could
OL,9,Fhave been - and should have been -
OL,10,Fprevented."
OL,12,FHe placed blame on those who had
OL,13,Fresponsibility for AR's care - his
OL,14,Fparents, schools, agencies,
OL,15,Findividuals and authorities - and said
OL,16,Fwhile the teenager's "trajectory
OL,17,Ftowards grave violence was signposted
OL,18,Frepeatedly and unambiguously", those
OL,19,F"responsible for safeguarding the
OL,20,Fpublic did not act with the cohesion,
OL,21,Furgency or clarity required."
OL,26,@xD@VOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FConcluding the failure by agencies to
OL,7,Ftake responsibility, he added: "The
OL,8,Ffrankly depressing and therefore
OL,9,Furgent matter... is this failure - at
OL,10,Fan organisation and individual level -
OL,11,Fto stand up and accept responsibility
OL,12,Ffor managing the risk AR posed.
OL,14,F"Far too often AR's 'case' was passed
OL,15,Ffrom one public sector agency to
OL,16,Fanother in an inappropriate merry-go-
OL,17,Fround of referrals, assessments, case
OL,18,Fclosures and hand offs."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FMoving to his parents, Sir Adrian said
OL,7,Fthey were ready to "excuse and defend"
OL,8,Ftheir son's actions, failing to "stand
OL,9,Fup to his behaviour and set
OL,10,Fboundaries".
OL,12,FUltimately, he said, this led to their
OL,13,Ffailure to "do what they morally ought
OL,14,Fto have done" and report "the clear
OL,15,Fescalation of risk" in the week
OL,16,Fleading up to the attack.
OL,18,FIf they had, he said, "AR would not
OL,19,Fhave been at liberty to conduct the
OL,20,Fattack and it would not therefore have
OL,21,Foccurred".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FThe chair said while he recognised the
OL,7,Frole of AR's parents was "complex"
OL,8,Fthey - particularly his dad - "created
OL,9,Fsignificant obstructions to
OL,10,Fconstructive engagement with AR by the
OL,11,Fvarious agencies the were involved".
OL,13,FWhat were the five fundamental
OL,14,Fproblems found in the report?
OL,16,FAddressing other failings found during
OL,17,Fthe inquiry, Sir Adrian said there had
OL,18,Fbeen a "repeated tendency" by multiple
OL,19,Fagencies to excuse the killer's
OL,20,Fbehaviour on the basis of his autism
OL,21,Fspectrum disorder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,F"Regularly used his autism as an
OL,7,Fexplanation or even excuse for his
OL,8,Fconduct, including his violence," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "This was both unacceptable and
OL,10,Fsuperficial".
OL,12,FEven when it was recognised, Sir
OL,13,FAdrian noted, it was never properly
OL,14,Fidentified as a factor which
OL,15,F"significantly increased the risk he
OL,16,Fposed".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]wD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FBut, Sir Adrian also made it clear it
OL,7,Fwould be "entirely wrong" to make a
OL,8,Fgeneral association between autism and
OL,9,Fan increased risk of violent harm to
OL,10,Fothers.
OL,12,FThe inquiry heard from more than 100
OL,13,Fwitnesses, 67 who gave live evidence,
OL,14,Fabout topics including AR's
OL,15,Finvolvement with health services,
OL,16,Fsocial care and education, and the
OL,17,Fthree referrals to anti-terror
OL,18,Fprogramme Prevent which were made, and
OL,19,Fclosed, before he carried out the
OL,20,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FThe report listed hundreds of
OL,7,Frecommendations - some urgent while
OL,8,Fothers, it said, require longer-term
OL,9,Fstructural reform.
OL,11,FThe chair said Phase Two - which will
OL,12,Fbe shaped by his findings in Phase One
OL,13,F- will address the adequacy of multi-
OL,14,Fagency systems to address the risk
OL,15,Fposed by young people whose fixation
OL,16,Fwith and desire to commit acts of
OL,17,Fextreme violence presents a
OL,18,Fsignificant risk to public safety.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,F"Detailed consideration should be
OL,7,Fgiven to restructuring fundamentally
OL,8,Fthe way that our society handles those
OL,9,Fwho pose a real risk of killing or
OL,10,Fcausing serious harm to others," he
OL,11,Fsaid in his conclusions.
OL,13,FHe also said Phase Two should
OL,14,F"consider whether there should be
OL,15,Ffurther ability to restrict or monitor
OL,16,Faccess to the internet on the part of
OL,17,Fchildren and young people, if there is
OL,18,Fconcern they pose a risk to others."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776172268
OL,3,C'Evident high level of danger' posed
OL,4,Cby the Southport killer not appreciated
OL,6,FOn his recommendations, Sir Adrian
OL,7,Fsaid, those requiring immediate action
OL,8,Fwas "for the government to decide
OL,9,Fwhether to accept them, reject them,
OL,10,For adopt an alternative course".
OL,12,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
